Package monero.wallet.model

Class MoneroTxQuery

java.lang.Object
monero.daemon.model.MoneroTx
monero.wallet.model.MoneroTxWallet
monero.wallet.model.MoneroTxQuery
All Implemented Interfaces:
Filter<MoneroTxWallet>
public class MoneroTxQuery extends MoneroTxWallet implements Filter<MoneroTxWallet>
Configures a query to retrieve transactions. All transactions are returned except those that do not meet the criteria defined in this query.
